reviewText: South side Johnny  and the dukes in fine form . You get 2 concerts. These guys play  good time Rock N Roll music with great songs. And if you buy a  DVD player that plays all regions you will  never have to worry about regions again Also the price was so good I ordered a second copy.  You get a lot of songs and their all brilliant . These guys deserve more credit.
This dvd is in a European format. Disappointed because I really wanted to see it .
